events.name: 移動（ラストダンジョン４）

parameters: \C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Luna, I told you that you have no chance of winning."

Sylvia: "You were the only student I ever acknowledged as a genius magician. You
were exceptional even among the students."
Sylvia: "But I never thought you would betray Lucia and turn against her."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Shut up. I'm not interested in your old stories."

Sylvia: "Hehehe... I knew we needed a sacrifice to lure you out here. Mao and
Mei served that purpose."

Sylvia: "The Knights of Messiah didn't lend you their power, did they? We don't
even know where Regnus Grahardt is."

Sylvia: "So, Luna, now is the perfect time to crush you. It's best to nip
troublesome buds like you in the bud."

Sylvia: "If we leave you be, your comrades might get killed somewhere again,
right? You have no choice but to fight recklessly, do you?"
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I thought I never wanted to hear that voice again."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Sylvia, the leading magician of Valentina... Your cowardice is as strong as
ever. Can't you crush a former student's spirit without resorting to such
underhanded tactics?"
Sylvia: "The former student has become quite cheeky, hasn't she?"

Sylvia: "Hilda is currently the top student at Valentina Magic School. I've
appointed Hilda as the general of Valentina."

Sylvia: "Ideally, Luna, after you quit being Lucia's attendant, I wanted to
invite you. You were supposed to do Hilda's job."

Sylvia: "Hehe... In other words, Hilda is your creation. If you had become the
general of Valentina, Mao and Mei wouldn't have been eaten by Hilda."
[Hilda] "Luna, Mao and Mei's flesh was delicious, you know?"

[Hilda] "I swallowed them whole from head to toe, sucking on their bones and
all."

[Hilda] "Especially their eyeballs were crunchy and truly delectable. Thank you
for the meal."

[Hilda] "They were so delicious that I made them into hamburgers and saved them.
Want to try Mao and Mei's hamburgers?"
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "I warned you before, didn't I? If you interfere any further, you'll suffer."
Sylvia: "First, you'll fight Hilda and the top magicians of Valentina."

Sylvia: "Needless to say about Hilda, but she is on a different level from
anyone you've fought before."

Hilda: "Heeheehee... I'll force you to eat Mao and Mei's meatballs at the moment
of your death. Ahahahaha!"
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Hilda... I will make you suffer before I kill you...!"

Sylvia: "It was I who ordered Hilda, but you know. Fufufu... Those two, until
the very end, they were calling out for Luna and begging for help, even as they
turned into lumps of flesh."

Sylvia: "The look on the brother's face when his sister was eaten first was
priceless. The very image of despair. Oh, how pitiful... kukuku."

Sylvia: "The hamburgers really were delicious. I'll let Luna have them raw,
especially."
\I[89]HINT: "There is a 'Last Defeat Erotic Scene' in the battle against Hilda."

\I[89]HINT: "If you are defeated, it will lead to the 'Last Defeat Erotic Scene'. You
can choose to view the Last Defeat Erotic Scene before the battle as well."
\I[89]HINT: "Would you like to view the 'Last Defeat Erotic Scene'?"
Watch (Surrender. \I[7]View the final defeat erotic scene.)
見る(敗北する。\I[7]ラスト敗北エロを見る。)
Sylvia: "I didn't expect Hilda to lose now. This was unforeseen."

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "After all, Luna is the top magician that I personally appointed. It's not
strange for her to defeat Hilda."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "Luna, I'll give you one last chance."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "If you want, I can let you escape now?"

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] "I just thought that by letting you go, we could find Regnus Grahardt. This
battle has no benefit for me."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "Despite your final warning, I have no intention of running away."
